snippet.title: Let's Play Slime Rancher on Xbox One: YOU DISGUST ME SLIMES
snippet.description:
In Slime Rancher on Xbox One (free this month in Xbox's Games with Gold scheme) you play a slime-wrangling slime rancher, capturing slimes for your up-and-coming slime farm. A slime is a kind of space hopper that eats and poops. Subscribe for more Xbox One gameplay on Outside Xbox? http://www.tinyurl.com/SubToOxbox

Your primary farming implement in Slime Rancher is your Vacpack: a farming gun that sucks up slimes, slime food and slime by-products (plorts), then shoots those same items wherever you aim them. 

Your slime rancher farming business is based on selling these plorts for cash. Who is buying plorts? Why are they buying them? Do we want to even know? Answers in the comments, if you'd be so kind.
